column2: The Champerret Heliopolis offers charm and tranquility in the heart of Paris' 17th Arrondissement near Espace Champerret and Porte Maillot conference center.

Düsseldorf 1995 is located in Düsseldorf, just 2.4 miles from Central Station Düsseldorf and 2.8 miles from Südpark. The property is around 2.9 miles from Theater an der Kö, 3 miles from Königsallee, and 3.1 miles from German Opera on the Rhine.
